@node "main" "AmiSystemRestore"
@{fg fill}@{u}AmiSystemRestore@{uu}@{fg text}
  r1 beta7 (22.08.2013)
  by Christopher Handley

This is a @{b}public beta@{ub} of AmiSystemRestore.  But as no stability problems have been reported (despite more than a year of public use), I will probably be making it non-beta within the next few releases.  Thank you to everyone who has tested it.


AmiSystemRestore was written using PortablE.

For changes in this release, please read the @{"13. History" link "13_0"} chapter.

